==Personal life==
On April 29, 2024, it was confirmed that Kim would marry model and actress [[Kim Jin-kyung]] in June.<ref>{{Cite web|last=Kim|first=Ji-hye|date=April 29, 2024|title=김진경 측 "축구선수 김승규와 올 6월 결혼"[공식입장]|trans-title=Kim Jin-kyung’s side “We will marry soccer player Kim Seung-gyu this June” [Official statement]|url=https://m.entertain.naver.com/article/112/0003694399|access-date=April 29, 2024|publisher=HeraldPop|language=ko|via=[[Naver]]}}</ref> The couple married on June 17, 2024 in [[Seoul]].<ref>{{Cite web|last=Jo|first=Min-jeong|date=June 18, 2024|title=손흥민-조규성, 이현이까지? 톱스타 총출동한 김진경♥김승규 결혼식 현장|trans-title=Son Heung-min, Jo Kyu-sung, and even Lee Hyun-i? Kim Jin-kyung♥Kim Seung-gyu wedding scene full of top stars|url=https://www.chosun.com/entertainments/enter_general/2024/06/18/MFVCH5XLOWIS477SWEF7Z5ELRI/|access-date=June 18, 2024|publisher=[[The Chosun Ilbo|Chosun]]|language=ko}}</ref>

